
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p>BabesForBitcoin.com (hereinafter referred to as “BabesForBitcoin.com” or the “Website”).</p>
			<p>THIS PRIVACY POLICY GOVERNS YOUR USE OF THE WEBSITE, WHICH IS PROVIDED BY BFB, THE OWNER OF THE WEBSITE. BY ACCESSING THE WEBSITE, YOU ARE INDICATING YOUR ACKNOWLEDGEMENT AND ACCEPTANCE OF THIS PRIVACY POLICY. THIS PRIVACY POLICY IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE BY BFB AT ANY TIME IN ITS SOLE DISCRETION. YOUR USE OF THE WEBSITE AFTER SUCH CHANGES ARE IMPLEMENTED CONSTITUTES YOUR ACKNOWLEDGEMENT AND ACCEPTANCE OF THE CHANGES. PLEASE CONSULT THIS PRIVACY POLICY REGULARLY.</p>
			<p>NOTE: Our privacy policy is null and void in cases of fraud!</p>
			<p>This policy explains the privacy practices for BFB LLC, a Delaware limited liability company and owner of the Website, (hereinafter referred to as “BitFunding LLC”, “BFB”, “our”, “we”, or “us”). In order to provide interactive computer billing and avoid fraud, BFB collects and uses certain information about you. This policy explains what we collect, what we use and how you can interact with BFB in order to ensure the accuracy of the data we collect and use.</p>
			<ol>
				<li>
					<h2>1) Information Collection:</h2>
					<p>Visitors can access our Website home page and browse certain public areas of our Website without disclosing any personal data. However, in order to provide you with a particular product or service online, BFB may request that you voluntarily supply BFB with primary personal data (such as name, address, telephone number and email address) and identifiers (such as Website password). BFB gives you the option of using a secure transmission method for sending such information.</p>
					<p>BFB receives and stores all information that you enter in our Website and billing pages. In addition, BFB collects information about you during your visit, such as your IP Address. Additionally, when becoming a Model of the Website, BFB requires a valid government issued ID to verify that you are over 18 years old. You are required to provide BFB with accurate and up-to-date information, and failure to provide BFB with such information could result in voiding your Agreement with BFB.</p>
					<p>You can inquire about your personal data by sending an e-mail to policies@BabesForBitcoin.com. Within a week, BFB shall provide you with a readable copy of the personal data which BFB keeps about you. BFB charges a $25 processing fee for the request. Prior to completing your request, BFB may require that you provide BFB with proof of your identity. BFB reserves the right to refuse any request for information though BFB will communicate the reason for its decision.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>2) Information Use:</h2>
					<p>BFB is the sole owner of the information collected on its sites. BFB will not sell, share, or rent this information to third parties in ways different from what is disclosed in this policy. BFB shall release data when required by law, to enforce its Agreement or the contract rights of its clients. BFB shares the following data with the owner/operator of the Website from which you are purchasing goods and services utilizing BFB services: the URL you are purchasing goods or services from, your e-mail address, your name, your address, your phone number, your date of birth, and your agreement to be bound by BFB terms and conditions. BFB uses the data it collects for the technical administration of the Website, research and development, and fraud deterrence.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>3) Information sharing:</h2>
					<p>BFB does not rent, sell and/or share information about you with other people or nonaffiliated companies, except that we may provide information about you under the following circumstances:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>A. BFB provides the information to trusted partners who work on behalf of or with BFB under confidentiality agreements. These companies do not have any independent right to share this information.</li>
						<li>B. BFB responds to subpoenas, court orders, or legal process, or to establish or exercise BFB's legal rights or defend against legal claims;</li>
						<li>C. BFB believes it is necessary to share information in order to investigate, prevent, or take action regarding illegal activities, suspected fraud, situations involving potential threats to the physical safety of any person, violations of the Website's Terms of Service, or as otherwise required by law; and/or,</li>
						<li>D. BFB transfers information about you if BFB is acquired by or merged with another company. In this event, BFB will notify you before information about you is transferred and becomes subject to a different Privacy Policy.</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>4) Email correspondence:</h2>
					<p>BFB may request a confirmation when you receive and open an e-mail communication delivered by BFB. We archive and identify the origination IP address of all email sent into our network.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>5) Third party information:</h2>
					<p>Occasionally, BFB receives information from third parties to compare it to information that you had provided to BFB for fraud prevention purposes.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>6) Cookies:</h2>
					<p>A cookie is a piece of data stored on the visitor's hard drive containing information about the visitor. BFB employs “cookie” technology. We use Cookie to store personal data, to authenticate you as a Site user, for security purposes, and to track our affiliate click-throughs and sign-up rate.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>7) Children:</h2>
					<p>BFB does not request, or knowingly collect, personal data from anyone under the age of 18. Furthermore, BFB does not knowingly give children the ability to post messages or otherwise distribute information about themselves on our Website.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>8) Security:</h2>
					<p>We take every precaution to protect our visitors' information. We have implemented security policies, rules and technical measures to protect the personal data that we have under our control from unauthorized access, improper use or disclosure, unauthorized modification, unlawful destruction, or accidental loss. BFB utilizes Secure Socket Layer (SSL) software when receiving and transmitting electronic payments. BFB encrypts the information that you provided.</p>
					<p>In addition, BFB does everything to protect your information off-line. All employees and data processors who have access to, and are associated with, the processing of personal data are obliged to respect the confidentiality of our visitors' personal data. BFB employs a username and password scheme in order to limit and achieve access to our computer network by our employees and third parties.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<h2>9) Correction/Updating Personal Information:</h2>
					<p>You may access certain information about you for the purpose of viewing, updating, and in some instances deleting from our system any information deemed inaccurate. You may request to access your information by sending a request to <a href="mailto:policies@BabesForBitcoin.com">policies@BabesForBitcoin.com</a></p>
					<p>If you have an inquiry or concern about our privacy policy, please contact us at the above address.</p>
				</li>
			</ol>
